					<description><![CDATA[<p>Eight eligible Mayo Clinic hospitals earned A grades from&amp;#160;The Leapfrog Group, an independent national nonprofit organization that provides safety ratings. All eight hospitals have maintained straight A’s since spring 2022. Notably, Mayo Clinic in Arizona is among just 11 hospitals in the nation that have achieved an A in every Leapfrog grading cycle since 2012 [&amp;#8230;]</p>
